_______________________________________________________________________________
"Precognition"      
        This allows a psionicist to fortell the future.  "What will I
        find if I enter the next room?".  It will tell the number of
        inanimate objects, the number of living objects, and how many
        of those living objects are hostile.
 
SP Cost:  20		Guild Level:  2		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  precognition <direction>
